Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:29.83,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:31.55,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:36.89,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.67,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:40.03,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葬仪社吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:42.91,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要放跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.07,0:13:51.98,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:05.32,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
