Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:21:59.09,song_CN_ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}我明明知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.28,0:22:02.48,song_CN_ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}今天却还是许下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:09.00,song_CN_ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}无法实现的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:14.31,song_CN_ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}不要松开
